#: energy.cpp:121
msgid "&Enable Display Energy Saving"
msgstr "&Yenza uboniso lwamandla olugcinwayo"

#: energy.cpp:124
msgid "Check this option to enable the power saving features of your display."
msgstr "Khangela olu khetho ukwenza imisebenzi esemqoka igcineke yoboniso lwakho."

#: energy.cpp:127
msgid "Your display has NO power saving features!"
msgstr "Umboniso wakho awunamandla akugcina misebenzi esemqoka!"

#: energy.cpp:138
msgid "&Standby after:"
msgstr "&Mela omnye emva:"

#: energy.cpp:140 energy.cpp:151 energy.cpp:163
msgid " min"
msgstr " min"

#: energy.cpp:141 energy.cpp:152 energy.cpp:164
msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "Ikhubazekile"

#: energy.cpp:144
msgid ""
"Choose the period of inactivity after which the display should enter "
"\"standby\" mode. This is the first level of power saving."
msgstr ""
"Khetha ithuba lokungasebenzi emva kokuba isiboniso sizakungena \"omeleyo\" "
"indlela. Lo ngumphakamo wokuqala wokugcina amandla."

#: energy.cpp:149
msgid "S&uspend after:"
msgstr "&Gxotha emva:"

#: energy.cpp:155
msgid ""
"Choose the period of inactivity after which the display should enter "
"\"suspend\" mode. This is the second level of power saving, but may not be "
"different from the first level for some displays."
msgstr ""
"Khetha ithuba lokungasebenzi emva kokuba isiboniso sizakungena \"gxotha\" "
"indlela. Lo ngumphakamo wesibini ukugcina amandla, kodwa ayinaku banamahluko "
"ukusuka kumphakamo woluhlu wezinye iziboniso."

#: energy.cpp:161
msgid "&Power Off after:"
msgstr "&Susa amandla emva:"

#: energy.cpp:167
msgid ""
"Choose the period of inactivity after which the display should be powered "
"off. This is the greatest level of power saving that can be achieved while "
"the display is still physically turned on."
msgstr ""
"Khetha ithuba lokungasebenzi emva kokuba isiboniso sinokubanamandla "
"asuswayo. Lo ngumphakamo omkhulu ukugcina amandla aokusetyenziswa ngexesha "
"isiboniso sisasetyenziswayo."

#: energy.cpp:397
msgid ""
"<h1>Energy Saving For Display</h1> If your display supports power saving "
"features, you can configure them using this module.<p> There are three "
"levels of power saving: standby, suspend, and off. The greater the level of "
"power saving, the longer it takes for the display to return to an active "
"state.<p> To wake up the display from a power saving mode, you can make a "
"small movement with the mouse, or press a key that is not likely to cause "
"any unintended side-effects, for example, the \"shift\" key."
msgstr ""
"<h1>Ugcino lwamandla okubonisa</h1> Ukuba isiboniso sakho sixhasa ugcino "
"lwamandla omsebenzi osemqoka, ungawaqwalasela usebenzisa lo mnqongo.<p> "
"Kukho imiphakamo emithathu ogcino lwamandla: omeleyo, gxotha, kwaye yeka. "
"Umphakamo omkhulu wogcino lwamandla, okuye ikuthatha ukubonisa ukubuyisela "
"kwindawo esebenzayo.<p> Ukuvusa isiboniso kwindlela yogcino lwamandla, "
"ungenza intshukumo encinane ngemouse, okanye cinezela isitshixo "
"esingenakubangela naliphi na icala elingenzi nto-iziqhamo, umzekelo, "
"isitshixo i \"shift\"."
